Remove outer leaves from Tanimura & Antle Sweet Gem(tm) lettuce, and set aside. Chop Tanimura & Antle Sweet Gem(tm) lettuce hearts. Mix together: chopped Tanimura & Antle Sweet Gem(tm) lettuce hearts, green onion, snow peas, green pepper, broccoli, vinaigrette salad dressing and fresh garlic. Season with pepper and serve equal portions of the chopped green salad on beds of Sweet Gem(tm) Lettuce leaves.